{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">This Is A FPS Looter Shooter Game.</h2>Players assume the role of survivors in a post-apocalyptic world.<br><br><strong>Core Gameplay: </strong>Scavenge, Fight, Escape, Craft, and Weapon Modification.<br><br><strong>Gameplay Loop: </strong>Explore adventure zones to scavenge resources, defeat or avoid enemies, interact with other survivors, and escape with loot back to the safehouse. Craft equipment, modify weapons, and build character abilities in the safehouse. Venture into more dangerous areas to acquire superior loot.<br><br>In short, this is a post-apocalyptic survival game featuring scavenging, zombie combat, crafting, weapon modification, character ability building, permanent death, camp management and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gunsmith system, for crafting imaginative weapons exclusive to you<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/Gunsmith_System.gif?t=1725854920\" /><br></li><li> Map exploration and map random features<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/Evacuate_System.gif?t=1725854920\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/Day-Night_Cycle_System.gif?t=1725854920\" /><br></li><li> Various types of enemies such as zombies, mutated zombies, humans, etc<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/AI_Vertical_Movement.gif?t=1725854920\" /><br></li><li> A variety of firearms, melee, and thrown weapons<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/Weapons.gif?t=1725854920\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057710/extras/Attachments.gif?t=1725854920\" /><br><i